reviewText: The DVD was new in excellent condition and the picture and sound qualities were great! No complaints here.
Played awesome for an old tv horror classic , No issues , Thank You !

OMG!  Do I remember this movie triology!  I remember crawling between the sofa and wall to watch it while peeking around the corner back when I was 20 . . . the third one . . . was delighted to find it.  my daughter remembered watching it with me years later.
cult movie trilogy, ecspecially great if your a Karen Black fan
Excellent movie. I loved Karen Black's acting in this film. A must see for horror fans.
